name: 2 Bed - Modern - Clean living space Prudential #16
description: 2 Bed apartment on Clearway street in Boston by Boston Furnished Rooms is a modern furnished living space for you, your family and friends to enjoy. It is also perfect for business accommodation. This apartment features clean, modern amenities, gourmet kitchen, central heat and air conditioning, wifi and cable. Located right in downtown, this place is close to Prudential, Fenway Park, Newbury Street, walking distance to subway/train stations, 6km from Logan airport.
